  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h3>We are passionate about helping you to achieve your ambitions and our courses are consistently recommended by students and employers.</h3>
<p>We work closely with universities and employers to ensure that our courses are designed with your career in mind. In doing so, we ensure that you will gain the qualifications, skills and confidence you need to be successful in your chosen field.</p>
<h3>Why choose us?</h3>
<p>We are the number one choice for many adult learners in Essex because we offer:</p>
<ul>
<li>Value for money</li>
<li>Dedicated, friendly teaching staff with industry experience in the subjects they teach</li>
<li>Qualifications accredited by leading professional bodies</li>
<li>Courses eligible for <a data-udi="umb://document/84a65ba9c08c480198c48a867663fbc2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/84a65ba9c08c480198c48a867663fbc2}" title="Advanced Learner Loan">Advanced Learner Loans</a> that don’t need to be paid back until you earn more than £25,000 per year. Even better, if you study an Access course you could effectively study for FREE!*</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/59855863215f4729823c4972d56ddb58" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59855863215f4729823c4972d56ddb58}" title="Financial Support">Financial support</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/006980f67003439e88ae4df4f9f05d19" href="/{localLink:umb://document/006980f67003439e88ae4df4f9f05d19}" title="Career Advice">careers advice and guidance</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/a498f0f5b18b42f89b0f404a85c50afc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a498f0f5b18b42f89b0f404a85c50afc}" title="Wellbeing and Counselling">wellbeing support</a></li>
<li>A convenient location, located just off the A13, with free parking (subject to availability).</li>
</ul>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e79b618c70b546ac830cfe50829da246" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79b618c70b546ac830cfe50829da246}" title="Our Adult courses">Discover our courses</a> </h4>
<h6>*Access to HE students could be eligible for an Advanced Learner Loan which will be written off by the Government once they've finished their Higher Education qualification.</h6>]]></mainContent>
